-- Bolivia Walks Out of Informal Talks at Cancun Climate Summit, Mexico Says
-- B y   C a r l o s   M a n u e l   R o d r i g u e z
-- 2010-12-09T02:08:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-09/bolivia-walks-out-of-informal-talks-at-cancun-climate-summit-mexico-says.html
Bolivia walked out of informal talks
at the United Nations climate summit in Cancun, Mexico, Luis
Alfonso del Alba, a Mexican negotiator, told a media briefing.  No other country followed Bolivia and the South American
nation remains part of the formal talks, Del Alba said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carlos Manuel Rodriguez in Mexico City at 
